{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "93f4f052-722f-4052-afc2-16719bada187",
    "name": "TerkOffice 07: Terk the Raven",
    "sceneId": "60cb5886-83dd-4e8f-9953-a9eafd43c179",
    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "6a12b275-b990-4eaa-974b-6ef32605a693",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d2f39b21-eb10-4000-b183-edd8712e6c7d",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "I had a meeting with your patron over the break. He's extremely displeased that Gerhard remains at the school, and this is clearly your fault.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a944eb23-55d5-448c-ba2a-252409d88a6e",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "What did you find in Gerhard's office? There must be something useful hidden there.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "7a73dc37-7539-4443-a69f-4dd00dcbd05c",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "657a366b-057f-4da1-8151-fb0f9f5bd4cf",
                            "text": "Tell the Truth",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "43203105-a6b1-49a2-ba0d-df74a9e375de",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "90",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7e0462ff-4846-47b4-b689-e2569e045821",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I tried everything I can, but I still can't break into Gerhard's office. The Master has his door so booby-trapped, I can't get close to disarming and unlocking the door.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dc97b684-cc07-4b59-ac0b-9b0ae5ed0f37",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Worthless! You aren't even a good thief! ",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "2",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "2feb3e70-c2eb-48fb-b2e8-7bafa779d964",
                            "text": "Bluff",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "319b8aa3-3910-4a3d-a6f2-1a1695ca7bfa",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "I've looked in every nook and cranny of Gerhard's office, but I haven't found anything useful. There's just nothing there.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "65772217-4b7d-4266-83e0-103c61756700",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Did you search in his file cabinet?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "df055f7c-129e-4979-a96c-02cd58e974f8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "Oh yes, I searched through every file he has.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c39efb34-5da2-4371-b030-ae045ef15d9b",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Gerhard doesn't have a file cabinet in his office! I've spoken to him about his lack of organization in the past!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fe587a31-9945-4c51-9e0e-efbecbf10170",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "So, admit it - you haven't actually searched Gerhard's office, have you?",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2d0585cd-4fba-44a1-a687-47367f847078",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "No sir. I can't get past the trap on the door.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "26317db0-3f55-414d-b7fc-ad7f73d88e56",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "7861d4c3-59cf-463c-9cfb-111012fad870",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "90",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "698b5ce5-2380-4bd5-91f5-628cf630bb2f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "text": "What's the matter, Mr. Terk? Is my Patron getting tired of you wasting his time with meaningless reports? Sounds like the Headmaster is, too.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4213f1ab-a4d9-4d7f-931f-d6dec6a33790",
                                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This is YOUR fault! You lazy incompetent hooligan - you were supposed to get rid of Gerhard by now! I knew you couldn't do anything right.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "3",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "16ec3caf-61ea-4e8d-ad72-d3c6adb20180",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Your Patron is a very dangerous person. If you don't find what he wants soon, I may... You may learn just how dangerous he can be.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5fee332f-a4a6-4a76-ae05-2cf55945d405",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Your patron seems to think that Gerhard has some sort of Raven statue hidden here at the school. Look for it.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d7bf4058-33fe-4e80-b6fc-bbf82003ac22",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "If you can't break into Gerhard's office soon, then we'll just have to find a different way. For now though, keep an eye out for the Raven.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.incrementTime",
                    "id": "75d9bdd1-011e-4be4-94be-5b965f7c1544",
                    "days": 0,
                    "hours": 0,
                    "minutes": "30"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "0e64c208-b108-4568-a168-27ba7eff38be",
                    "name": "Gerhard has the Raven???",
                    "description": "According to Terk, my Patron is looking for the Raven and thinks Gerhard has hidden it somewhere. Interesting. No wonder Gerhard talked about it in class. Well, I've pretty much searched this school and I haven't seen it anywhere.\n\nIf the Raven is anywhere around here, it's probably in Gerhard's office. Shame I can't open the door. I guess Terk is going to find out how dangerous my Patron is when I don't find the Raven."
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeScene",
                    "sceneId": "f1d169df-e10e-451d-8481-0d0290b7cbbe",
                    "spawnId": "2e1c2cd6-e8d8-4d69-8c37-68f7b246bb96",
                    "fadeTime": 2
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}